<A>__{in the back seat is whittlesley. early 40's, the wreck of a once handsome man. unshaven. sweat stained. rail thin. scratches on his arms, a fresh scar on one cheek. as the taxi roars downhill towards the harbor, whittlesley leans over the front seat. (italics indicate portuguese to be subtitled)}
